- (Nora): Hello?

23:53.933 --> 23:57.134
Anybody there?

23:58.704 --> 24:00.805
No looters.

24:00.807 --> 24:03.541
- Well, if a Walmart is a 10

24:03.543 --> 24:06.043
on the
attractiveness-to-looters scale,

24:06.045 --> 24:08.479
